documentation.text: WXDAI token index in the curve's 3pool
USDC token index in the curve's 3pool
Max amount of USDC spend each time rmmDeposit() or rmmRepay is called, should be close to rent amount
Mapping of whitelisted addresses that can call deposit or repay (ie: Gelato contract...)

@dev Swap USDC to Wxdai from Curve 3pool and deposit on RMM LendingPool
 @notice Swap USDC to Wxdai and deposit on RMM
 Emit a Deposit event
 Requirements:
 - `msg.sender` must be whitelisted
 - `owner` must have enough USDC
 - `owner` must have allowed enough USDC to smartContract

@dev Swap USDC to Wxdai from Curve 3pool and repaid loan on RMM
 @notice Swap USDC to Wxdai and repaid on RMM
 Emit a Repaid event
 Requirements:
 - `msg.sender` must be whitelisted
 - `owner` must have enough USDC
 - `owner` must have xDai Borrowing
 - `owner` must have allowed enough USDC to smartContract

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

redeemTokens().details: Transfer every USDC or WxDai stuck on the contract to the owner

params._addressIndex: the index of address in the whitelistAddresses array Requirements: - `msg.sender` must be the owner - `_addressIndex` must exists

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

rmmDeposit().details: Swap USDC to Wxdai from Curve 3pool and deposit on RMM LendingPool

rmmRepay().details: Swap USDC to Wxdai from Curve 3pool and repaid loan on RMM

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._address: the address to be whitelisted Requirements: - `msg.sender` must be the owner - `_address` must not be already whitelisted

redeemTokens().notice: Redeem USDC and WxDai to owner Emit a Repaid event Requirements: - `msg.sender` must be the owner

removeFromWhitelist(uint8).notice: Remove an address from the whitelist

rmmDeposit().notice: Swap USDC to Wxdai and deposit on RMM Emit a Deposit event Requirements: - `msg.sender` must be whitelisted - `owner` must have enough USDC - `owner` must have allowed enough USDC to smartContract

rmmRepay().notice: Swap USDC to Wxdai and repaid on RMM Emit a Repaid event Requirements: - `msg.sender` must be whitelisted - `owner` must have enough USDC - `owner` must have xDai Borrowing - `owner` must have allowed enough USDC to smartContract

setMaxUsdcAmountToSpend(uint256).notice: Update the maximum USDC amount to be spent Requirements: - `msg.sender` must be the owner
